snippet.title: Em-A-Li Official Trailer | Portal Inspired Horror
snippet.description:
Inspired by portal, Em-A-Li is an advance artificial health care provider or “wife bot” designed to take care of their master. It was created solely for the purpose of cooking, cleaning, and comfort. But what happens when an A.I. doesn’t follow its protocols? Play as Li and escape the rooms you are trapped in. You may uncover a darker story than the possibility of an A.I. gone rogue…

Game Page: https://yobobgames.com/

Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/YobobGames
